      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">Join us in powering a sustainable future with solar and battery storage solutions.</p>
      <a href="#job-openings" class="px-8 py-3 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition-colors duration-200" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">Explore Opportunities</a>
    </div>
