    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6" data-aos="fade-up">Ready to Shape the Future?</h2>
    <p class="text-xl mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">Be a part of our mission to deliver sustainable energy solutions.</p>
    <a href="mailto:careers@solvaris.com" class="px-8 py-3 bg-white text-green-800 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-200" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">Apply Today</a>
